lead_paragraph: An article yesterday about Senator Dianne Feinstein's decision against running for governor of California misstated the situation of State Senator John Vasconcellos. Mr. Vasconcellos, a Democrat, is exploring the possibility of running; he has not declared his candidacy.
abstract: Correction of Jan 21 article on Sen Dianne Feinstein's decision not to run for California governor
